{"lastModified":1775138906974,"uri":"c::10120242293::vessel::d5cca4a7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nLAGOON 620 Opal is a stunning luxury catamaran that redefines elegance and performance on the water, with spacious living areas, 5 guests’ cabins and outdoor entertainment on flybridge as well in cockpit with comfortable seating ideal for dining or enjoying the view. If you are feeling more adventurous there is a range of water toys including paddleboards, snorkeling gear, and water skis. \n\nWith its Expansive 18.90-meter length and 10-meter beam, it offers spacious living areas, five double guest cabins with en-suite bathrooms, and ample storage for up to 10 guests. A professional crew of three ensures personalized service throughout your journey. \n\nRelax on the flybridge with sunbathing areas, a shaded dining space, and ambient lighting, or enjoy the variety of water toys, including stand-up paddleboards, snorkeling gear, and water skis.\n  \nThe yacht features a hydraulic bathing platform, high-speed Wi-Fi, a fully equipped galley, and premium entertainment systems. \n\nThe name \"Opal\" evokes elegance and rarity, inspired by the gemstone known for its captivating play of colors. It symbolizes beauty, sophistication, and uniqueness, reflecting the yacht's luxurious features and exceptional presence on the water. \n","blueprint":{"name":"OPAL","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca4a7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::708eca20-fdc7-11ef-a2c8-2bd12a9cceb7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca4a7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::709050c0-fdc7-11ef-a2c9-2bd12a9cceb7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca4a7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::dcPJ2Hbbr.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca4a7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::70929ab0-fdc7-11ef-be0c-ef0866361730/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca